      description : "AOSX-14-000050 - The macOS system must limit the number of concurrent SSH sessions to 10 for all accounts and/or account types."
      info        : "Operating system management includes the ability to control the number of users and user sessions that utilize an operating system. Limiting the number of allowed users and sessions per user is helpful in reducing the risks related to DoS attacks.

